English:
This has got to be it.
Okidoke. I'll see what I can do.
Chinese:
不會錯！就是這個……
等一下，我探查看看。
Korean:
틀림없어, 이거야…
어디, 한번 봐 볼까
German:
Das müssen sie sein.
Na gut. Dann schau ich mal, was ich tun kann.

English:
Hmm. It's not protected at all...
But there's hardly any data here...
Chinese:
嗯……有受到保護……
而且裡面的容量幾乎是空的……
Korean:
응, 프로텍트는 안 걸려있군…
그보다, 용량이 거의 텅 비어 있어…
German:
Hm. Überhaupt nicht geschützt ...
Aber hier sind kaum Daten ...

English:
Wait, what's this?
I'm getting some weird feedback.
Does this link to somewhere else?
Chinese:
嗯？
這個奇妙的手感是什麼……有連接到其他地方嗎？
Korean:
하지만, 대체 뭐지…?
이 미묘한 반응… 어딘가로 링크되어 있는 건가…?
German:
Moment, was ist das?
Da ist dieses komische Feedback.
Führt dieser Link irgendwohin?

English:
Watch out, [p]!
I accessed something strange on the other end of
that link.
Chinese:
喂！[p]！小心！
我不小心點到奇怪的連結了……
Korean:
야, 조심해 [p]!!
링크 너머의 이상한 것에 접속해 버렸어…
German:
Pass auf, [p]!
Am anderen Ende dieses Links bin ich auf
etwas Seltsames gestoßen.
